        {
            "body": "<p>The following granted power replaces the bit of luck power of the Luck domain.</p>", 
            "name": "Replacement Power", 
            "sections": [
                {
                    "body": "<p id=\"malign-eye\">As a standard action, you can afflict one target within 30 feet with your malign eye, causing it to take a &ndash;2 penalty on all saving throws against your spells. The effect lasts for 1 minute or until the target hits you with an attack. You can use this ability for a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Wisdom modifier.</p>", 
